# Important note about animation

`mechanism.get_animation()` internally uses **Matplotlib `FuncAnimation`**, so the animation runs when the figure window opens.

If nothing moves, try forcing the backend:

```python
import matplotlib
matplotlib.use("TkAgg")
```

at the top of the script.

